name: InfieldNews.com
overview:
InfieldNews.com (http://www.infieldnews.com) is a baseball news feed service that gives fans an easy way track their favorite teams and players.

InfieldNews.com uses a powerful content aggregation engine to deliver the hottest & most interesting baseball news from thousands of online sources including Blogs, News Sites, Twitter, Facebook and more.

Through voting and discussion, fans decide whatâ€™s interesting. Stories that receive positive community feedback rise up towards the #1 slot so each team, player or game feed is constantly evolving to deliver the most interesting content.

InfieldNews.com collects player quotes from all media sources across the Internet. When a player is quoted in the media InfieldNews.com presents the quote on the site for fans to discuss.
